### ========================================================
### Task Management System
### ========================================================

### --------------------------------------------------------
### Task - GET ALL
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

### Task - GET BY ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

### Task - POST
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "New Task",
  "dueDate": "2026-12-01",
  "completed": false
}

### Task - PUT
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Task",
  "dueDate": "2027-01-15",
  "completed": true
}

### Task - PATCH
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "completed": true
}

### Task - DELETE
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

### --------------------------------------------------------

### BillableTask - GET ALL
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/billable
Accept: application/json

### BillableTask - GET BY ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/billable/1
Accept: application/json

### BillableTask - POST
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/billable
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "New Billable Task",
  "dueDate": "2026-12-15",
  "completed": false,
  "hourlyRate": 150.00
}

### BillableTask - PUT
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/billable/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Billable Task",
  "dueDate": "2027-01-20",
  "completed": true,
  "hourlyRate": 200.00
}

### BillableTask - PATCH
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/billable/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "hourlyRate": 175.00
}

